rows.label: tlk44200181_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Teos Aure is an amazing place, don't
you think?

rows.label: tlk44200181_01_msg0002
rows.name:
I read about Alst's cities in books
and encyclopedias, but they don't
seem nearly as pretty as here.

rows.label: tlk44200181_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I just don't get why everyone's all kind
of gloomy.

rows.label: tlk44200181_01_msg0004
rows.name:
My grandma and grandpa always
look sort of miserable...

rows.label: tlk44200181_01_msg0005
rows.name:
It's weird, because if they love the
city like I do, they should be happy,
all day, every day!
